## Syntax
```
chmod [OPTIONS] [PERMISSIONS] [FILE]
```

## Access Roles
```
owner

group

other
```

## Access Modes
```
read(r)

write(w)

execute(x)
```

## Listing permissions
```
ls -l
```

# Changing File and Folder Access Permissions
## Adding Permissions
```
chmod [user]+[accessmode]
```
## Removing Permissions
```
chmod [user]-[accessmode]
```
